{"tid":994078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好玩唔玩走去玩屎] 男子承認機場馬桶蓋上大解再用手塗抹廁板　罰款六千元","createTime":"2019-01-24T11:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T14:35:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b4aed4c1bedad524aefb90fb9839450e2a3065b2","tid":994078,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"一名無業男子自上星期三起連續4日，在機場客運大樓不同男廁的馬桶蓋上大解，其後再用手將糞便塗抹於廁板。機場職員知悉事件後，憑閉路電視認出這名男子，在他再出現時，報警將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n這名男子在西九龍裁判法院承認5項扔棄垃圾、吐痰或其他不合衛生的行為罪名，他求情時表示感到後悔，承諾不會再犯，但未有透露為何要這樣，被判罰款6000元。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，事發在上星期三至六，職員憑閉路電視影像鎖定56歲被告任子健為嫌疑人，被告再度出現時，職員持圖片上前查問，被告直認不諱。警方接報到場調查，被告在警誡下承認所有案情。"},{"pid":"561e9367c82b762999a9154df29acb98b7262c94","tid":994078,"uid":21629,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cac3a5b9f87e6cae740edd76fe033fb59563cf6","tid":994078,"uid":138594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"用手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8485a3de4fb30520092716af0a945b1b103339aa","tid":994078,"uid":118709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"地鐵都見好多人Hi啲鼻屎落扶手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6d3c9f99c2fcc91b7a0a9a570e6ed5cbe8f02b","tid":994078,"uid":29070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"痴線 屎都好玩"},{"pid":"33b2ea488d5f7200e0847b87382bf27a1d51fe9e","tid":994078,"uid":124107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"re